{"tid":993181,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"何謂抄歌？","createTime":"2019-01-23T17:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T01:39:08.000Z","uid":137006,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"657dd3573a60fd09a827de7731c74a83a7940c4e","tid":993181,"uid":137006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"自己唔係好敢話係音樂人<br />\n但會寫下歌編吓曲<br />\n<br />\n呢個問題其實困擾咗我好耐<br />\n對你地而言到底何謂抄歌？<br />\n<br />\n舊嘅代表有Mr.  高/連登仔都算 &rdquo;公認&rdquo; 佢地 &rdquo;抄&rdquo;<br />\n而大多數人係因為首Mr Tam嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Melody</span>同It&rsquo;s my life 好似<br />\n所以斷定佢地抄<br />\n新嘅代表有Eason 嘅可一可再嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Melody</span>同一首韓國歌好似<br />\n所以又斷定佢抄<br />\n<br />\n但一首歌除咗唱嘅Melody<br />\n仲有其他樂器嘅melody<br />\n但點解有時結他solo嘅licks一樣又冇人話抄？<br />\n同樣係一首歌入面嘅melody<br />\n唔係人唱所以唔係抄？<br />\n<br />\n除melody外<br />\n一首歌嘅編曲都好重要<br />\n但流行曲十首有七八首編曲都差唔多<br />\n鼓beat又唔太大分別咁又算唔算抄？<br />\n<br />\n定係其實，抄唔抄係好主觀<br />\n你一聽就feel倒好似某首歌就係抄<br />\n佢聽唔倒似就唔係抄？<br />\n<br />\n見連登最近又討論翻抄歌呢樣野<br />\n而且見倒抄歌呢樣野係直接影響音樂人嘅發展<br />\nMr為例，俾人話抄歌就收咗皮。<br />\n所以想理解吓大家對抄歌嘅定義<br />\n<br />\n對我而言，其實係冇抄歌呢回事<br />\n只要唔係犯咗抄歌嗰條法例(我記得係有，但唔記得詳細)<br />\n外界一聽認為嗰首新作品好似某首舊作品<br />\n咁樣只係新作品嘅作者&rdquo;實力&rdquo;未夠創作出<br />\n&ldquo;最原創&rdquo;嘅歌<br />\n並唔係新作品作者 &rdquo;人格有問題&rdquo; 去抄歌<br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06c0d77ead9e984f180e540cabeade028b28485","tid":993181,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"大陸例子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UW047XUVeKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUW047XUVeKI&d=abUks92o3xd5TFNNtPNxLv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=cfa462ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UW047XUVeKI</a><br />\n嘻唰唰 by 花兒樂隊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hoWynebkAtM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhoWynebkAtM&d=abUks92o3xd5TFNNtPNxLv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5af59bdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hoWynebkAtM</a><br />\nK2g by Puffy Amiyumi<br />\n<br />\n個主唱公開認左佢抄歌, 華語樂壇我諗無第二個敢抄完再公開認<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f169b3264900e0b3143437d57a940742f49984f8","tid":993181,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06c0d77ead9e984f180e540cabeade028b28485","tid":993181,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"大陸例子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UW047XUVeKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUW047XUVeKI&d=abUks92o3xd5TFNNtPNxLv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=cfa462ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UW047XUVeKI</a><br />\n嘻唰唰 by 花兒樂隊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hoWynebkAtM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhoWynebkAtM&d=abUks92o3xd5TFNNtPNxLv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5af59bdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hoWynebkAtM</a><br />\nK2g by Puffy Amiyumi<br />\n<br />\n個主唱公開認左佢抄歌, 華語樂壇我諗無第二個敢抄完再公開認<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:47:52.000Z","msg":"大張偉抄開歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5607f18ed34da8728ce85210c5b60ad9eab646","tid":993181,"uid":137006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06c0d77ead9e984f180e540cabeade028b28485","tid":993181,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"大陸例子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UW047XUVeKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUW047XUVeKI&d=abUks92o3xd5TFNNtPNxLv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=cfa462ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UW047XUVeKI</a><br />\n嘻唰唰 by 花兒樂